"āmantraṇasabhājane | āpracchannam" ity amaraḥ || "āṅi nupracchacor upasaṅkhyānam" ity ātmanepadam || sakhitvaṃ nirvāhayati—kāla iti || kāle kāle pratiprāvṛṭkālam | suhṛtsamāgamanakālaś ca kālaśabdenocyate | vīpsāyāṃ dviruktiḥ || bhavataḥ saṃyogaṃ samparkam etya ciravirahajam uṣṇaṃ bāṣpam ūṣmāṇaṃ netrajalaṃ ca || "bāṣpo netrajaloṣmaṇoḥ" iti viśvaḥ || muñcato yasya śalasyaḥ snehavyaktiḥ premāvirbhāvo bhavati | snigdhānāṃ hi ciravirahasaṅgatānāṃ bāṣpapāto bhavatīti bhāvaḥ ||

<commentary>samprati tasya mārgaṃ kathayati—mārgam iti || he jalada, tāvad idānīṃ kathayataḥ | matta iti śeṣaḥ | tvatprayāṇasyānurūpam anukūlaṃ mārgam adhvānam || "mārgo mṛgapade māsi saumyarthe 'nveṣaṇe 'dhvani" iti yādavaḥ | śṛṇu | tad anu mārgaśravaṇānantaraṃ śrotrābhyāṃ peya pānārham | atitṛṣṇayā śrotavyam ity arthaḥ || peyagrahaṇāt sandeśasyāmṛtasāmyaṃ gamyate || me sandeśaṃ vācikam || "sandeśavāgvācikaṃ syāt" ity amaraḥ || śroṣyasi | yatra mārge khinnaḥ khinno 'bhīkṣṇaṃ kṣīṇabalaḥ san || "nityavīpsayoḥ" iti nityārthe dvirbhāvaḥ || śikhariṣu parvateṣu padaṃ nyasya nikṣipya | punarbalalābhārthaṃ kvacid viśramyety arthaḥ | kṣīṇaḥ kṣīṇo 'bhīkṣṇaṃ kṛśāṅgaḥ san | atrāpi kṛdantatvāt pūrvavad dviruktiḥ || srotasāṃ parilaghu gurutvadoṣarahitam | upalāsphālanakheditatvāt pathyam ity arthaḥ | tathā ca vāgbhaṭaḥ—"upalāsphālanakṣepavicchedaiḥ kheditodakāḥ | himavan malayodbhūtāḥ pathyā nadyo bhavanty amūḥ ||" iti || payaḥ pānīyam upabhujya śarīrapoṣaṇārtham abhyavahṛtya ca gantāsi gamiṣyasi || gamer luṭ ||</commentary>

adrer iti || pavano vāyur adreś citrakūṭasya śṛṅgaṃ harati kiṃsvit || kiṃsvicchabdo vikalpavitarkārthādiṣu paṭhitaḥ || iti śaṅkayonmukhībhir unnatamukhībhiḥ || "svāṅgāc copasarjanād asaṃyogopadhāt" iti ṅīṣ | mugdhābhir mūḍhābhiḥ "mugdhaḥ sundaramūḍhayoḥ" ity amaraḥ |
